<div style="position: relative; height: 15px; width: 100%;">  <a style="float: right;" href="?subtopic=creatures&race=orcwarlord">next <img src="images/arrow_right.gif" width="15" height="11" border="0"/></a>  <a style="position: absolute;" href="?subtopic=creatures&race=orcshaman"><img src="images/arrow_left.gif" width="15" height="11" border="0"/> previous</a>  <div style="position: absolute; width: 80%; margin-left: 10%; margin-right: 10%; text-align: center;"><a href="?subtopic=creatures"><img src="images/arrow_up.gif" width="11" height="15" border="0"/> back</a></div></div><div style="position: relative; top: 25px; clear: both; "><div style="height: 64px; margin-bottom: 5px;">  <h2 style="float: right;">Orc Spearmen</h2>  <img src="images/library/orcspearman.gif"/></div><div style="margin-bottom: 35px; clear: both;">  <p>Orc Spearmen are the distance fighters among the orcs. Their spears are deadly weapons, but they are weak short-range fighters. Usually, they are accompanied by other types of orcs, so that they can hide behind them and attack their enemies from the second row.</p>  <p>Orc Spearmen have 105 hitpoints. They are strong against energy and holy damage. On the other hand, they are weak against death and earth damage. It takes 310 mana to summon or convince these creatures.</p>  <p>Orc Spearmen yield 38 experience points. They carry gold coins, meat, spears, studded legs and sometimes other items with them.</p>  </div></div>